00:32:04,912 --> 00:32:07,878
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I may have found
the next piece to the puzzle.</i></font>

402
00:32:07,881 --> 00:32:10,615
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Ancient drawings hint
to the location of the tomb</i></font>

403
00:32:10,617 --> 00:32:13,819
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>and an elaborate door
to keep her contained.</i></font>

404
00:32:13,821 --> 00:32:17,256
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I've found a way
to decipher the codes.</i></font>

405
00:32:17,258 --> 00:32:19,526
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I'm sure I can get to her.</i></font>

406
00:32:28,002 --> 00:32:30,468
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>The ancient
Nihongi chronicles state</i></font>

407
00:32:30,470 --> 00:32:32,372
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>that within the tomb,</i></font>

408
00:32:32,374 --> 00:32:35,507
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>one must face
the "Ordeals of Himiko."</i></font>

409
00:32:35,509 --> 00:32:38,776
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Cross the Chasm of Souls,</i></font>

410
00:32:38,778 --> 00:32:42,017
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>pray to survive
the faces of Himiko,</i></font>

411
00:32:43,919 --> 00:32:49,021
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>behold her army
of a thousand handmaidens,</i></font>

412
00:32:49,023 --> 00:32:51,690
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>descend upon
Himiko's final resting place,</i></font>

413
00:32:51,692 --> 00:32:53,961
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>unleashing her scourge.</i></font>

414
00:33:04,972 --> 00:33:06,905
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>July 6th. I'm convinced</i></font>

415
00:33:06,907 --> 00:33:08,775
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>that my progress
is being monitored.</i></font>

416
00:33:09,344 --> 00:33:11,143
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I know them by name now...</i></font>

417
00:33:11,144 --> 00:33:12,877
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>The Order of Trinity.</i></font>

418
00:33:12,880 --> 00:33:14,948
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>An ancient
militant organization</i></font>

419
00:33:14,950 --> 00:33:17,815
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>that seeks control
over the supernatural</i></font>

420
00:33:17,817 --> 00:33:20,118
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>to rule the fate of mankind.</i></font>

421
00:33:20,121 --> 00:33:22,454
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>What if Himiko is the weapon</i></font>

422
00:33:22,457 --> 00:33:24,659
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>that Trinity has been seeking?</i></font>

423
00:33:34,434 --> 00:33:35,804
<font color="#FFFFFF">Can't sleep?</font>

424
00:33:40,976 --> 00:33:42,411
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's beautiful.</font>

425
00:33:45,247 --> 00:33:47,112
<font color="#FFFFFF">Enjoy it
while you can.</font>

426
00:33:47,114 --> 00:33:48,981
<font color="#FFFFFF">We're headed into the most
dangerous stretch of water</font>

427
00:33:48,983 --> 00:33:51,685
<font color="#FFFFFF">between Hong Kong
and California.</font>

428
00:33:52,752 --> 00:33:55,457
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your dad sure knew
how to pick a holiday.</font>

429
00:33:57,724 --> 00:34:01,862
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah. He had a knack for
the unexpected. Apparently.</font>

430
00:34:05,865 --> 00:34:08,400
<font color="#FFFFFF">I am starting to wonder
if he'd gone mad, though.</font>

431
00:34:10,237 --> 00:34:12,869
<font color="#FFFFFF">He didn't seem to know what
was real and what wasn't,</font>

432
00:34:12,871 --> 00:34:17,476
<font color="#FFFFFF">obsessing over some
ancient Japanese death queen.</font>

433
00:34:17,478 --> 00:34:20,079
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey, some men
like dangerous women.</font>

434
00:34:20,081 --> 00:34:22,914
<font color="#FFFFFF">Some men are foolish.</font>

435
00:34:22,916 --> 00:34:24,550
<font color="#FFFFFF">What?</font>

436
00:34:24,552 --> 00:34:28,088
<font color="#FFFFFF">Good night, Lu Ren.
Sweet dreams.</font>

437
00:34:44,405 --> 00:34:46,338
<font color="#FFFFFF">Not William Tell yet,
but you're close.</font>

438
00:34:46,340 --> 00:34:48,541
<font color="#FFFFFF">William Tell was a myth, Dad.</font>

439
00:34:48,543 --> 00:34:51,413
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, all myths
have foundation in reality.</font>

440
00:34:52,612 --> 00:34:54,347
<font color="#FFFFFF">I have to head off, sprout.</font>

441
00:34:54,349 --> 00:34:56,114
<font color="#FFFFFF">But you've only
just come back.</font>

442
00:34:56,115 --> 00:34:58,652
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I'll be back before...
- I even know you're gone.</font>

443
00:35:00,521 --> 00:35:02,355
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ana will keep an eye on you.</font>

444
00:35:02,356 --> 00:35:04,688
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't need one of
your employees babysitting me.</font>

445
00:35:04,690 --> 00:35:06,795
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can take care of myself.</font>

446
00:35:12,134 --> 00:35:13,568
<font color="#FFFFFF">My girl.</font>

447
00:35:16,036 --> 00:35:17,204
<font color="#FFFFFF">Lara</font>

448
00:35:22,177 --> 00:35:23,978
<font color="#FFFFFF">Never forget Dad loves you.</font>

449
00:35:25,047 --> 00:35:26,181
<font color="#FFFFFF">I know.</font>

450
00:36:12,458 --> 00:36:14,561
<font color="#FFFFFF">Thought that might wake you.</font>

451
00:36:15,230 --> 00:36:16,998
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your island's found us.</font>

452
00:36:21,902 --> 00:36:23,070
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yamatai.</font>

453
00:36:35,748 --> 00:36:38,583
<font color="#FFFFFF">We've lost all control!</font>

454
00:36:38,585 --> 00:36:40,784
<font color="#FFFFFF">- We need to abandon ship.
- What?</font>

455
00:36:40,786 --> 00:36:42,521
<font color="#FFFFFF">We're dead
in the water.</font>

456
00:36:42,523 --> 00:36:44,056
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's not gonna hold
much longer.</font>

457
00:36:44,057 --> 00:36:45,338
<font color="#FFFFFF">We need to get off
this boat now.</font>

458
00:37:01,342 --> 00:37:02,543
<font color="#FFFFFF">Wait!</font>

459
00:37:03,643 --> 00:37:05,177
<font color="#FFFFFF">Dad's papers!</font>

460
00:37:05,179 --> 00:37:07,282
<font color="#FFFFFF">Forget them! Lara!</font>

461
00:37:21,594 --> 00:37:22,829
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh!</font>

462
00:37:28,436 --> 00:37:30,139
<font color="#FFFFFF">Lara. Come on!</font>

463
00:37:37,378 --> 00:37:38,612
<font color="#FFFFFF">Lu!</font>

464
00:37:50,724 --> 00:37:52,327
<font color="#FFFFFF">The lifeboat!</font>

465
00:38:16,748 --> 00:38:18,085
<font color="#FFFFFF">Watch out!</font>

466
00:38:53,355 --> 00:38:54,422
<font color="#FFFFFF">Lu!</font>

467
00:38:56,389 --> 00:38:57,657
<font color="#FFFFFF">Lu!</font>

468
00:40:13,733 --> 00:40:15,135
<font color="#FFFFFF">Where am I?</font>

469
00:40:17,536 --> 00:40:20,438
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ah! She's awake.</font>

470
00:40:20,440 --> 00:40:23,144
<font color="#FFFFFF">I was beginning
to get worried about you.</font>

471
00:40:30,152 --> 00:40:31,186
<font color="#FFFFFF">A reef.</font>

472
00:40:32,253 --> 00:40:34,018
<font color="#FFFFFF">You hit it.</font>

473
00:40:34,019 --> 00:40:36,086
<font color="#FFFFFF">Thank God I found you.</font>

474
00:40:36,088 --> 00:40:38,990
<font color="#FFFFFF">Most people who try to
come here die in the currents.</font>

475
00:40:38,992 --> 00:40:41,695
<font color="#FFFFFF">Almost impossible to get here.</font>

476
00:40:42,128 --> 00:40:44,132
<font color="#FFFFFF">Even harder to leave.</font>

477
00:40:48,302 --> 00:40:49,403
<font color="#FFFFFF">Where's my...</font>

478
00:40:55,876 --> 00:40:57,144
<font color="#FFFFFF">Right here.</font>

479
00:41:03,882 --> 00:41:07,054
<font color="#FFFFFF">What are you doing here, Lara?</font>

480
00:41:10,791 --> 00:41:13,057
<font color="#FFFFFF">I have two daughters.</font>

481
00:41:13,059 --> 00:41:14,929
<font color="#FFFFFF">Dark hair like you.</font>

482
00:41:15,931 --> 00:41:17,864
<font color="#FFFFFF">Pretty like you.</font>

483
00:41:22,403 --> 00:41:26,105
<font color="#FFFFFF">Forgive me. Rude.</font>

484
00:41:26,106 --> 00:41:27,804
<font color="#FFFFFF">I haven't hosted a guest
here in a very long time.</font>

485
00:41:27,806 --> 00:41:30,476
<font color="#FFFFFF">My name is Mathias Vogel.</font>

486
00:41:34,581 --> 00:41:36,250
<font color="#FFFFFF">You must be hungry.</font>

487
00:41:40,588 --> 00:41:42,257
<font color="#FFFFFF">You know, I used to imagine</font>

488
00:41:43,456 --> 00:41:45,523
<font color="#FFFFFF">that I might find an ear</font>

489
00:41:45,525 --> 00:41:48,163
<font color="#FFFFFF">inside one of
those cans eventually.</font>

490
00:41:49,896 --> 00:41:52,396
<font color="#FFFFFF">Isn't that mad?</font>

491
00:41:52,398 --> 00:41:54,766
<font color="#FFFFFF">I guess being on this island
for so long</font>

492
00:41:54,768 --> 00:41:57,568
<font color="#FFFFFF">can make you a little crazy.</font>

493
00:41:57,570 --> 00:42:00,204
<font color="#FFFFFF">The only person
that I get to talk to</font>

494
00:42:00,206 --> 00:42:02,942
<font color="#FFFFFF">is on the other end
of this phone.</font>

495
00:42:02,943 --> 00:42:05,842
<font color="#FFFFFF">And they always say
the same thing...</font>

496
00:42:05,844 --> 00:42:09,282
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can't go home until
my work on the island is done.</font>

497
00:42:20,260 --> 00:42:22,260
<font color="#FFFFFF">What kind of work do you do?</font>

498
00:42:22,262 --> 00:42:26,199
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, a mix of things.
At the mercy of my employer.</font>

499
00:42:51,925 --> 00:42:53,592
<font color="#FFFFFF">You looking for this?</font>

500
00:42:56,195 --> 00:42:59,367
<font color="#FFFFFF">The machinations of fate
never cease to amaze me.</font>

501
00:43:01,201 --> 00:43:03,469
<font color="#FFFFFF">"The door to Himiko."</font>

502
00:43:05,871 --> 00:43:07,673
<font color="#FFFFFF">Richard had the entrance.</font>

503
00:43:11,043 --> 00:43:12,914
<font color="#FFFFFF">All that wasted time.</font>

504
00:43:15,983 --> 00:43:17,547
<font color="#FFFFFF">You have brought me the thing</font>

505
00:43:17,550 --> 00:43:20,583
<font color="#FFFFFF">that I most wanted
in this world.</font>

506
00:43:20,585 --> 00:43:21,621
<font color="#FFFFFF">Thank you.</font>

507
00:43:24,724 --> 00:43:27,327
<font color="#FFFFFF">What do you know
about my father?</font>

508
00:43:31,097 --> 00:43:32,998
<font color="#FFFFFF">Now I see the likeness.</font>

509
00:43:33,000 --> 00:43:36,501
<font color="#FFFFFF">The intelligence in the face.</font>

510
00:43:36,503 --> 00:43:38,405
<font color="#FFFFFF">The recklessness.</font>

511
00:43:44,378 --> 00:43:46,443
<font color="#FFFFFF">All he had to do
was cooperate.</font>

512
00:43:46,445 --> 00:43:49,447
<font color="#FFFFFF">Of course, being Richard,
he refused.</font>

513
00:43:49,449 --> 00:43:51,920
<font color="#FFFFFF">Thought he was saving
the world.</font>

514
00:43:52,186 --> 00:43:53,688
<font color="#FFFFFF">Where is he?</font>

515
00:43:58,192 --> 00:43:59,925
<font color="#FFFFFF">Where is he?</font>

516
00:43:59,927 --> 00:44:02,297
<font color="#FFFFFF">He's with God now.
I killed him.</font>

517
00:44:06,766 --> 00:44:10,405
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm sorry if I was too blunt.
I'm out of practice.</font>

518
00:44:11,038 --> 00:44:13,175
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's been seven years.</font>

519
00:44:14,574 --> 00:44:16,210
<font color="#FFFFFF">Seven years.</font>

520
00:44:29,655 --> 00:44:31,155
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on.</font>

521
00:44:31,157 --> 00:44:32,525
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on, come on!</font>

522
00:44:33,726 --> 00:44:35,594
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on. Get down there.</font>

523
00:44:41,936 --> 00:44:43,670
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get those skids moving!</font>

524
00:44:48,009 --> 00:44:49,440
<font color="#FFFFFF">Move.</font>

525
00:44:49,443 --> 00:44:50,610
<font color="#FFFFFF">Move!</font>

526
00:44:52,813 --> 00:44:54,514
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let's go!</font>

527
00:44:54,914 --> 00:44:56,746
<font color="#FFFFFF">Pick it up!</font>

528
00:44:56,748 --> 00:44:58,385
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on, go!</font>

529
00:45:01,588 --> 00:45:03,123
<font color="#FFFFFF">Tie her up!</font>

530
00:45:14,902 --> 00:45:17,070
<font color="#FFFFFF">Okay, winch it up!</font>

531
00:45:18,838 --> 00:45:20,306
<font color="#FFFFFF">Back to work.</font>

532
00:45:21,742 --> 00:45:24,143
<font color="#FFFFFF">Lara Croft.</font>

533
00:45:24,144 --> 00:45:26,612
<font color="#FFFFFF">You shouldn't have come here.</font>

534
00:45:27,246 --> 00:45:29,250
<font color="#FFFFFF">But I'm glad that you did.</font>

535
00:45:31,385 --> 00:45:34,922
<font color="#FFFFFF">Pack it up. We're moving camp!</font>

536
00:45:37,458 --> 00:45:41,858
<font color="#FFFFFF">- All right, let's pack it up!
- Okay, move out!</font>

537
00:45:41,860 --> 00:45:43,630
<font color="#FFFFFF">We're moving camp!</font>

538
00:45:50,804 --> 00:45:53,273
<font color="#FFFFFF">Keep it moving!
You, move!</font>

539
00:45:54,307 --> 00:45:55,574
<font color="#FFFFFF">Move it, move it.</font>

540
00:46:05,284 --> 00:46:07,418
<font color="#FFFFFF">Pick it up! Come on, let's go!</font>

541
00:46:07,420 --> 00:46:09,922
<font color="#FFFFFF">Who are these people?</font>

542
00:46:09,923 --> 00:46:13,393
<font color="#FFFFFF">Some are
shipwrecked fishermen.</font>

543
00:46:13,394 --> 00:46:16,128
<font color="#FFFFFF">And some paid smugglers
to take 'em to a better life.</font>

544
00:46:16,130 --> 00:46:18,231
<font color="#FFFFFF">Instead,
they brought 'em here.</font>

545
00:46:19,333 --> 00:46:22,233
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on!
We're backed up here. Move!</font>

546
00:46:22,235 --> 00:46:24,472
<font color="#FFFFFF">He said he killed my dad.</font>

547
00:46:27,706 --> 00:46:29,275
<font color="#FFFFFF">He killed mine.</font>

548
00:46:30,277 --> 00:46:31,512
<font color="#FFFFFF">They saw it.</font>

549
00:46:32,713 --> 00:46:35,182
<font color="#FFFFFF">Cold-blooded murder.</font>

550
00:46:35,547 --> 00:46:36,851
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm sorry.</font>

551
00:46:39,153 --> 00:46:42,619
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm sorry
that I brought you here.</font>

552
00:46:42,621 --> 00:46:46,458
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, you did take advantage
of a drunken sailor.</font>

553
00:46:48,260 --> 00:46:50,295
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on, move!</font>

554
00:46:50,297 --> 00:46:52,599
<font color="#FFFFFF">At least we're not dead yet.</font>

555
00:46:52,731 --> 00:46:54,201
<font color="#FFFFFF">No shit.</font>

556
00:47:41,215 --> 00:47:43,284
<font color="#FFFFFF">I need
some CL 20 up here!</font>

557
00:47:56,163 --> 00:47:57,463
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on, let's go!</font>

558
00:48:07,074 --> 00:48:09,440
<font color="#FFFFFF">You okay?</font>

559
00:48:09,443 --> 00:48:11,009
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get him up and back to work
right now.</font>

560
00:48:11,010 --> 00:48:12,811
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hang on.</font>

561
00:48:12,813 --> 00:48:14,773
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Right now!
- Let him rest. We'll manage.</font>

562
00:48:17,117 --> 00:48:18,614
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get him back
to work right now!</font>

563
00:48:18,617 --> 00:48:21,019
<font color="#FFFFFF">He's sick, man.
He needs to rest.</font>

564
00:49:17,443 --> 00:49:20,077
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get back to work!</font>

565
00:49:28,922 --> 00:49:31,057
<font color="#FFFFFF">You heard him!
Let's get back to work!</font>

566
00:49:38,932 --> 00:49:40,333
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey, Lara.</font>

567
00:49:40,335 --> 00:49:42,503
<font color="#FFFFFF">Lara! Get ready.</font>

568
00:49:43,336 --> 00:49:44,538
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey.</font>

569
00:49:46,405 --> 00:49:47,737
<font color="#FFFFFF">Go!</font>

570
00:49:47,739 --> 00:49:48,775
<font color="#FFFFFF">Go!</font>

571
00:50:08,929 --> 00:50:10,463
<font color="#FFFFFF">Look out!</font>

572
00:50:14,833 --> 00:50:16,570
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let's spread out!
Spread out!</font>

573
00:50:33,952 --> 00:50:35,420
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get her!</font>

574
00:50:35,422 --> 00:50:36,889
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get a move on!</font>

575
00:50:42,561 --> 00:50:43,795
<font color="#FFFFFF">Grab her!</font>

576
00:51:11,724 --> 00:51:15,126
<font color="#FFFFFF">She's in the river.
You want us to follow?</font>

577
00:51:15,128 --> 00:51:16,695
<font color="#FFFFFF">No.</font>

578
00:51:16,697 --> 00:51:18,931
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm sending Rocket
to track her.</font>

579
00:51:18,932 --> 00:51:22,568
<font color="#FFFFFF">If she survives,
he'll bring her back.</font>

580
00:54:06,733 --> 00:54:07,969
<font color="#FFFFFF">Really?</font>

581
00:58:23,722 --> 00:58:27,425
<font color="#FFFFFF">Easy now, easy.
I'm taking you back to camp.</font>

582
00:58:53,085 --> 00:58:54,954
<font color="#FFFFFF">Stop struggling!</font>

583
01:00:42,594 --> 01:00:43,596
<font color="#FFFFFF">Wait!</font>

584
01:00:55,641 --> 01:00:57,240
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, no, no, no!</font>

585
01:01:32,878 --> 01:01:35,445
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm not mad.
I'm not mad, I'm not mad.</font>

586
01:01:35,447 --> 01:01:37,682
<font color="#FFFFFF">Just ignore it. It'll go away.</font>

587
01:02:06,445 --> 01:02:07,447
<font color="#FFFFFF">Dad?</font>

588
01:02:10,081 --> 01:02:11,449
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's me.</font>

589
01:02:16,789 --> 01:02:18,954
<font color="#FFFFFF">Dad?</font>

590
01:02:18,956 --> 01:02:24,262
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's not real. Ignore it.
It'll go away. It always does.</font>

591
01:02:24,264 --> 01:02:26,664
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, look at me, look at me.</font>

592
01:02:26,666 --> 01:02:27,800
<font color="#FFFFFF">Please.</font>

593
01:02:33,371 --> 01:02:35,474
<font color="#FFFFFF">Do you remember this?
Do you remember:</font>

594
01:02:36,976 --> 01:02:38,378
<font color="#FFFFFF">We used to...</font>

595
01:02:46,552 --> 01:02:47,853
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's me.</font>

596
01:02:53,291 --> 01:02:54,760
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's Lara.</font>

597
01:03:01,699 --> 01:03:02,869
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sprout.</font>

598
01:03:07,606 --> 01:03:10,242
<font color="#FFFFFF">What the blazes
are you doing here?</font>

599
01:03:17,182 --> 01:03:18,751
<font color="#FFFFFF">Dad, I'm hurt.</font>

600
01:03:27,393 --> 01:03:28,760
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's all right.</font>

601
01:03:50,748 --> 01:03:52,447
<font color="#FFFFFF">This will hurt me
more than it hurts you.</font>

602
01:03:52,449 --> 01:03:54,217
<font color="#FFFFFF">What?</font>

603
01:03:54,219 --> 01:03:55,820
<font color="#FFFFFF">All right.</font>

604
01:03:56,422 --> 01:03:58,891
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're all right.
You're all right.</font>

605
01:04:00,192 --> 01:04:02,293
<font color="#FFFFFF">All right. It's all right.</font>

606
01:04:03,163 --> 01:04:05,465
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's done.</font>

607
01:04:17,842 --> 01:04:19,311
<font color="#FFFFFF">Rest now.</font>

608
01:04:23,447 --> 01:04:25,351
<font color="#FFFFFF">Will you stay with me?</font>

609
01:04:27,221 --> 01:04:28,956
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm not going anywhere.</font>

610
01:05:01,153 --> 01:05:04,391
<font color="#FFFFFF">Vogel! We found it! Yeah!</font>

611
01:05:07,293 --> 01:05:11,530
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah! Come on! We found it!</font>

612
01:05:18,469 --> 01:05:20,269
<font color="#FFFFFF">I found it.</font>

613
01:05:20,271 --> 01:05:22,007
<font color="#FFFFFF">Send the transport.</font>

614
01:06:01,980 --> 01:06:03,612
<font color="#FFFFFF">I thought you'd gone.</font>

615
01:06:03,614 --> 01:06:05,016
<font color="#FFFFFF">Usually when I see you
on this island,</font>

616
01:06:05,018 --> 01:06:06,518
<font color="#FFFFFF">it's you who disappears.</font>

617
01:06:30,309 --> 01:06:31,842
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let me do that.</font>

618
01:06:33,112 --> 01:06:34,447
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come here.</font>

619
01:06:40,818 --> 01:06:43,755
<font color="#FFFFFF">So, sprout,
where did you end up?</font>

620
01:06:44,523 --> 01:06:46,925
<font color="#FFFFFF">Did you go
to Oxford or Cambridge?</font>

621
01:06:49,628 --> 01:06:51,695
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on, which was it?</font>

622
01:06:51,697 --> 01:06:53,532
<font color="#FFFFFF">You know what, Dad?</font>

623
01:06:54,632 --> 01:06:57,668
<font color="#FFFFFF">I didn't go to university.</font>

624
01:06:57,670 --> 01:07:01,371
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, there's time yet.
You're still only a child.</font>

625
01:07:01,373 --> 01:07:05,342
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, I was a child
when you left me.</font>

626
01:07:05,344 --> 01:07:06,713
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ah, careful.</font>

627
01:07:14,753 --> 01:07:17,719
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hardest day of my life</font>

628
01:07:17,722 --> 01:07:20,425
<font color="#FFFFFF">when I gave up
trying to get back to you.</font>

629
01:07:24,630 --> 01:07:27,431
<font color="#FFFFFF">But I realized
she'd never let me leave.</font>

630
01:07:30,702 --> 01:07:34,375
<font color="#FFFFFF">What are you talking about?
Who's "she"?</font>

631
01:07:34,773 --> 01:07:36,041
<font color="#FFFFFF">Himiko.</font>

632
01:07:37,976 --> 01:07:41,179
<font color="#FFFFFF">Trinity had sent Vogel
to find her tomb</font>

633
01:07:41,181 --> 01:07:43,646
<font color="#FFFFFF">so that he could wake her
and get her power.</font>

634
01:07:43,648 --> 01:07:45,583
<font color="#FFFFFF">I had to stop them.</font>

635
01:07:47,320 --> 01:07:49,585
<font color="#FFFFFF">Right.</font>

636
01:07:49,588 --> 01:07:52,324
<font color="#FFFFFF">Vogel can't find the tomb
without me.</font>

637
01:07:52,326 --> 01:07:54,891
<font color="#FFFFFF">And since I'm dead</font>

638
01:07:54,893 --> 01:07:57,998
<font color="#FFFFFF">and since you've burnt
the rest of my research,</font>

639
01:07:58,597 --> 01:08:00,465
<font color="#FFFFFF">he'll never find it.</font>

640
01:08:02,235 --> 01:08:03,467
<font color="#FFFFFF">So...</font>

641
01:08:05,137 --> 01:08:06,670
<font color="#FFFFFF">About that.</font>

642
01:08:08,773 --> 01:08:10,739
<font color="#FFFFFF">What part of
"burn all my papers"</font>

643
01:08:10,742 --> 01:08:12,876
<font color="#FFFFFF">did you not understand?</font>

644
01:08:12,878 --> 01:08:16,413
<font color="#FFFFFF">If I'd burned the papers,
I wouldn't have found you.</font>

645
01:08:16,416 --> 01:08:19,882
<font color="#FFFFFF">I set diversions and false
leads wherever I could.</font>

646
01:08:19,885 --> 01:08:22,519
<font color="#FFFFFF">I watched for years
as they got it wrong.</font>

647
01:08:22,520 --> 01:08:24,354
<font color="#FFFFFF">And now you lead them
by the hand.</font>

648
01:08:24,356 --> 01:08:28,627
<font color="#FFFFFF">So a gun-toting psychopath
finds some ancient remains.</font>

649
01:08:29,394 --> 01:08:31,161
<font color="#FFFFFF">So what?</font>

650
01:08:31,162 --> 01:08:33,363
<font color="#FFFFFF">If Vogel opens that tomb,</font>

651
01:08:33,365 --> 01:08:36,967
<font color="#FFFFFF">Himiko's curse will be
unleashed on the world.</font>

652
01:08:36,970 --> 01:08:38,635
<font color="#FFFFFF">Dad, listen...</font>

653
01:08:38,636 --> 01:08:41,840
<font color="#FFFFFF">You coming here was a mistake.</font>

654
01:08:47,645 --> 01:08:50,279
<font color="#FFFFFF">I came here to find out
what happened to you.</font>

655
01:08:50,282 --> 01:08:52,118
<font color="#FFFFFF">So long as the tomb was safe,</font>

656
01:08:52,617 --> 01:08:54,818
<font color="#FFFFFF">you were safe.</font>

657
01:08:54,819 --> 01:08:57,556
<font color="#FFFFFF">I was trying to keep you safe.</font>

658
01:08:59,225 --> 01:09:00,990
<font color="#FFFFFF">But I underestimated your...</font>

659
01:09:00,993 --> 01:09:02,128
<font color="#FFFFFF">My what?</font>

660
01:09:04,662 --> 01:09:06,664
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Stupidity?
- No.</font>

661
01:09:10,403 --> 01:09:12,038
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your bravery.</font>

662
01:09:18,077 --> 01:09:20,210
<font color="#FFFFFF">We have to get off
this island.</font>

663
01:09:20,212 --> 01:09:21,877
<font color="#FFFFFF">There's no way off, Lara.</font>

664
01:09:21,878 --> 01:09:23,814
<font color="#FFFFFF">Vogel's got a satellite phone.</font>

665
01:09:23,815 --> 01:09:25,582
<font color="#FFFFFF">We can get to it.
We can call for help.</font>

666
01:09:25,583 --> 01:09:27,317
<font color="#FFFFFF">Vogel has an army.</font>

667
01:09:27,319 --> 01:09:29,621
<font color="#FFFFFF">You were the one who taught me
to never give up.</font>

668
01:09:32,925 --> 01:09:35,094
<font color="#FFFFFF">That was a different time.</font>

669
01:09:36,595 --> 01:09:38,797
<font color="#FFFFFF">When I was a different man.</font>

670
01:09:50,876 --> 01:09:53,744
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Lara.
- Well, I'm still his daughter.</font>

671
01:09:55,180 --> 01:09:56,515
<font color="#FFFFFF">Lara!</font>

672
01:10:19,503 --> 01:10:20,872
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on!</font>

673
01:10:43,828 --> 01:10:45,595
<font color="#FFFFFF">Try another combination.</font>

674
01:10:45,596 --> 01:10:48,698
<font color="#FFFFFF">And another one,
and another one.</font>

675
01:10:56,909 --> 01:11:00,243
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on. Come on,
give me the damn code.</font>

676
01:11:11,090 --> 01:11:13,855
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey. We're trying
the explosives again.</font>

677
01:11:13,858 --> 01:11:15,391
<font color="#FFFFFF">Set another charge.</font>

678
01:11:15,394 --> 01:11:16,796
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes, boss.</font>

679
01:11:39,184 --> 01:11:41,783
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get over there.
Stop talking.</font>

680
01:11:55,167 --> 01:11:57,466
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get the guns.
I'm gonna get the sat phone.</font>

681
01:11:57,469 --> 01:11:59,734
<font color="#FFFFFF">Then we'll find a way for all
of us to get out of here.</font>

682
01:11:59,737 --> 01:12:01,337
<font color="#FFFFFF">We need to leave now.</font>

683
01:12:10,916 --> 01:12:13,953
<font color="#FFFFFF">Vogel! They re escaping!</font>

684
01:12:21,559 --> 01:12:23,095
<font color="#FFFFFF">Go!</font>

685
01:12:23,494 --> 01:12:25,331
<font color="#FFFFFF">Shoot them!</font>

686
01:12:41,613 --> 01:12:43,748
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Get them to safety.
- Okay.</font>

687
01:12:48,086 --> 01:12:50,720
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll be right behind you. Go.</font>

688
01:13:39,171 --> 01:13:40,703
<font color="#FFFFFF">Shit.</font>

689
01:13:51,615 --> 01:13:53,150
<font color="#FFFFFF">We have to move.</font>

690
01:13:53,484 --> 01:13:54,818
<font color="#FFFFFF">I have to wait here.</font>

691
01:13:54,819 --> 01:13:56,189
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm not leaving Lara behind.</font>

692
01:14:23,247 --> 01:14:25,385
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's beautiful,
isn't it, Richard?</font>

693
01:14:28,686 --> 01:14:30,420
<font color="#FFFFFF">I wish I would've known
that you were alive</font>

694
01:14:30,421 --> 01:14:32,224
<font color="#FFFFFF">all these years.</font>

695
01:14:33,158 --> 01:14:35,894
<font color="#FFFFFF">At least I would've had
somebody to talk to.</font>

696
01:14:48,771 --> 01:14:51,039
<font color="#FFFFFF">I need your help, Richard.</font>

697
01:14:51,042 --> 01:14:53,443
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get the door open for me.</font>

698
01:14:53,444 --> 01:14:55,677
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's been seven years.</font>

699
01:14:55,680 --> 01:14:57,447
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm going home
to see my family.</font>

700
01:14:57,448 --> 01:15:00,287
<font color="#FFFFFF">If I open that tomb,
you won't have a family.</font>

701
01:15:01,420 --> 01:15:02,921
<font color="#FFFFFF">Open it!</font>

702
01:15:04,356 --> 01:15:05,523
<font color="#FFFFFF">Open it!</font>

703
01:15:06,625 --> 01:15:07,827
<font color="#FFFFFF">Open it!</font>

704
01:15:08,594 --> 01:15:09,594
<font color="#FFFFFF">Never!</font>

705
01:15:12,829 --> 01:15:14,662
<font color="#FFFFFF">Have it your way.</font>

706
01:15:14,664 --> 01:15:17,836
<font color="#FFFFFF">With or without you,
I'm getting inside that tomb.</font>

707
01:15:26,412 --> 01:15:27,445
<font color="#FFFFFF">Put that down!</font>

708
01:15:29,948 --> 01:15:31,748
<font color="#FFFFFF">Put it down.</font>

709
01:15:32,682 --> 01:15:34,382
<font color="#FFFFFF">You don't think
I can pull this trigger</font>

710
01:15:34,385 --> 01:15:35,985
<font color="#FFFFFF">before you hit me
with that arrow.</font>

711
01:15:35,988 --> 01:15:37,555
<font color="#FFFFFF">Shoot him, Lara. Shoot him!</font>

712
01:15:38,122 --> 01:15:40,056
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on, put your weapon down.</font>

713
01:15:40,059 --> 01:15:42,328
<font color="#FFFFFF">Shoot him, Lara. We can't
let him get to Himiko.</font>

714
01:15:44,628 --> 01:15:47,497
<font color="#FFFFFF">You really don't believe
this nonsense, do you?</font>

715
01:15:47,498 --> 01:15:51,301
<font color="#FFFFFF">Tell your father to
open the door, or he's dead.</font>

716
01:15:51,304 --> 01:15:53,671
<font color="#FFFFFF">You can make him do it, Lara.</font>

717
01:15:54,340 --> 01:15:56,905
<font color="#FFFFFF">Transport's already
on its way.</font>

718
01:15:56,908 --> 01:15:59,876
<font color="#FFFFFF">We can all be
off this goddamn island.</font>

719
01:15:59,877 --> 01:16:01,578
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let him shoot me.</font>

720
01:16:01,579 --> 01:16:04,582
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sacrificing one life
is worth saving millions.</font>

721
01:16:07,052 --> 01:16:10,052
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's your decision.</font>

722
01:16:10,055 --> 01:16:11,890
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's your finger
that's pulling this trigger.</font>

723
01:16:18,130 --> 01:16:20,399
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I'm sorry.
- No.</font>

724
01:16:22,533 --> 01:16:25,670
<font color="#FFFFFF">I haven't come all this way
to see you die.</font>

725
01:16:31,844 --> 01:16:33,313
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll do it.</font>

726
01:16:38,449 --> 01:16:40,086
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll open it.</font>

727
01:16:44,887 --> 01:16:47,425
<font color="#FFFFFF">Finally, a Croft
with some sense.</font>

728
01:18:23,721 --> 01:18:25,256
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ladies first.</font>

729
01:18:52,217 --> 01:18:54,086
<font color="#FFFFFF">Mark the path.</font>

730
01:19:26,217 --> 01:19:28,319
<font color="#FFFFFF">She's still breathing.</font>

731
01:19:28,320 --> 01:19:30,953
<font color="#FFFFFF">Or it's a change in
atmospheric pressure.</font>

732
01:19:30,956 --> 01:19:32,423
<font color="#FFFFFF">Keep walking.</font>

733
01:19:49,108 --> 01:19:50,742
<font color="#FFFFFF">You should've seen
the look on your...</font>

734
01:20:04,588 --> 01:20:07,127
<font color="#FFFFFF">That wasn't designed
to keep people out.</font>

735
01:20:09,128 --> 01:20:11,159
<font color="#FFFFFF">That was put there
to keep people in.</font>

736
01:20:11,162 --> 01:20:12,396
<font color="#FFFFFF">Dad?</font>

737
01:20:46,229 --> 01:20:48,300
<font color="#FFFFFF">Chasm of Souls.</font>

738
01:21:44,189 --> 01:21:45,823
<font color="#FFFFFF">You go next.</font>

739
01:21:59,503 --> 01:22:03,608
<font color="#FFFFFF">"Pray to survive
the faces of Himiko."</font>

740
01:22:04,108 --> 01:22:05,509
<font color="#FFFFFF">We're getting closer.</font>

741
01:22:09,747 --> 01:22:14,250
<font color="#FFFFFF">"The Death Queen
turns day to night.</font>

742
01:22:14,252 --> 01:22:17,454
<font color="#FFFFFF">"She must die
to bring back life."</font>

743
01:22:23,061 --> 01:22:24,429
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, shit.</font>

744
01:22:36,407 --> 01:22:37,675
<font color="#FFFFFF">- The floor!
- Lara!</font>

745
01:22:47,451 --> 01:22:49,453
<font color="#FFFFFF">There's gotta be a way
to stop this.</font>

746
01:22:50,956 --> 01:22:52,456
<font color="#FFFFFF">Look around!</font>

747
01:22:54,393 --> 01:22:56,591
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on. Come on!</font>

748
01:22:56,594 --> 01:22:58,796
<font color="#FFFFFF">Vogel, what's going on?</font>

749
01:23:12,912 --> 01:23:14,277
<font color="#FFFFFF">"Pray to survive."</font>

750
01:23:14,279 --> 01:23:17,082
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's a keyhole. We need a key!</font>

751
01:23:18,283 --> 01:23:19,750
<font color="#FFFFFF">The prayer wheels!</font>

752
01:23:24,689 --> 01:23:25,722
<font color="#FFFFFF">Lara!</font>

753
01:23:30,395 --> 01:23:31,761
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's not working.</font>

754
01:23:31,762 --> 01:23:33,431
<font color="#FFFFFF">Check the other prayer wheels.</font>

755
01:23:34,300 --> 01:23:35,466
<font color="#FFFFFF">Try this!</font>

756
01:23:39,802 --> 01:23:41,139
<font color="#FFFFFF">No.</font>

757
01:23:41,305 --> 01:23:42,539
<font color="#FFFFFF">Wait.</font>

758
01:23:46,045 --> 01:23:47,046
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's a color puzzle.</font>

759
01:23:50,048 --> 01:23:53,315
<font color="#FFFFFF">"The Death Queen
turns the day to night."</font>

760
01:23:53,318 --> 01:23:55,752
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Black.
- Black! Here!</font>

761
01:23:57,421 --> 01:23:58,488
<font color="#FFFFFF">Shit!</font>

762
01:23:58,489 --> 01:23:59,724
<font color="#FFFFFF">Blue!</font>

763
01:24:01,326 --> 01:24:02,457
<font color="#FFFFFF">No!</font>

764
01:24:02,460 --> 01:24:03,729
<font color="#FFFFFF">Here!</font>

765
01:24:05,095 --> 01:24:06,497
<font color="#FFFFFF">It doesn't work.</font>

766
01:24:08,134 --> 01:24:09,135
<font color="#FFFFFF">Lara!</font>

767
01:24:16,341 --> 01:24:18,609
<font color="#FFFFFF">Last one! Yellow!</font>

768
01:24:25,548 --> 01:24:27,317
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's not working.</font>

769
01:24:27,319 --> 01:24:29,519
<font color="#FFFFFF">Just try them all, damn it!</font>

770
01:24:29,520 --> 01:24:32,453
<font color="#FFFFFF">"The Death Queen
turns the day to night."</font>

771
01:24:32,456 --> 01:24:34,289
<font color="#FFFFFF">"She must die
to bring back..."</font>

772
01:24:34,292 --> 01:24:35,556
<font color="#FFFFFF">"Life."</font>

773
01:24:35,559 --> 01:24:36,929
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on!</font>

774
01:24:38,729 --> 01:24:40,597
<font color="#FFFFFF">The color of life.</font>

775
01:24:46,436 --> 01:24:48,106
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm running out of floor!</font>

776
01:24:55,280 --> 01:24:56,614
<font color="#FFFFFF">Green!</font>

777
01:25:19,670 --> 01:25:22,436
<font color="#FFFFFF">You always were the brains
of the family, sprout.</font>

778
01:25:26,244 --> 01:25:28,546
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, let's get going, sprout.</font>

779
01:25:34,420 --> 01:25:35,921
<font color="#FFFFFF">Where's the floor?</font>

780
01:25:37,055 --> 01:25:38,055
<font color="#FFFFFF">Gone.</font>

781
01:25:52,270 --> 01:25:53,471
<font color="#FFFFFF">Flare.</font>

782
01:26:09,653 --> 01:26:11,521
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on, Lara.</font>

783
01:26:13,891 --> 01:26:15,127
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm going back for her.</font>

784
01:26:16,760 --> 01:26:18,328
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm coming with you.</font>

785
01:26:18,329 --> 01:26:20,166
<font color="#FFFFFF">You dad gave his life for us.</font>

786
01:26:58,069 --> 01:27:03,307
<font color="#FFFFFF">Himiko's army of
a thousand handmaidens.</font>

787
01:27:04,242 --> 01:27:07,574
<font color="#FFFFFF">They sacrificed themselves
in ritual suicide</font>

788
01:27:07,577 --> 01:27:09,880
<font color="#FFFFFF">to serve their queen
in the afterlife.</font>

789
01:27:15,752 --> 01:27:17,889
<font color="#FFFFFF">Exactly as your notes.</font>

790
01:27:20,425 --> 01:27:21,626
<font color="#FFFFFF">We found her.</font>

791
01:27:47,920 --> 01:27:51,222
<font color="#FFFFFF">All right, this is it.
We're finishing this.</font>

792
01:27:52,789 --> 01:27:54,957
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's not too late
to change your mind.</font>

793
01:27:54,960 --> 01:27:56,591
<font color="#FFFFFF">There's a very big difference</font>

794
01:27:56,594 --> 01:27:58,859
<font color="#FFFFFF">between myth and reality,
Richard.</font>

795
01:27:58,862 --> 01:28:01,832
<font color="#FFFFFF">Something that you could
never understand.</font>

796
01:28:02,731 --> 01:28:03,935
<font color="#FFFFFF">Gentlemen.</font>

797
01:28:22,220 --> 01:28:23,654
<font color="#FFFFFF">Open it.</font>

798
01:29:07,965 --> 01:29:11,600
<font color="#FFFFFF">You see? I told you there was
nothing to be afraid of.</font>

799
01:29:11,603 --> 01:29:13,435
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's just...</font>

800
01:29:13,436 --> 01:29:15,240
<font color="#FFFFFF">a little old lady.</font>

801
01:29:18,143 --> 01:29:20,011
<font color="#FFFFFF">Prepare her for transport.</font>

802
01:29:28,585 --> 01:29:30,421
<font color="#FFFFFF">Something doesn't add up.</font>

803
01:29:31,454 --> 01:29:34,826
<font color="#FFFFFF">She's not a monster
in any of these paintings.</font>

804
01:29:40,398 --> 01:29:43,434
<font color="#FFFFFF">It looks like she was
taking herself here.</font>

805
01:29:47,238 --> 01:29:48,872
<font color="#FFFFFF">Not being forced.</font>

806
01:29:51,109 --> 01:29:54,443
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>The Death Queen
turns day to night.</i></font>

807
01:29:54,444 --> 01:29:56,845
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>She must die
to bring back life.</i></font>

808
01:29:56,847 --> 01:29:58,417
<font color="#FFFFFF">"Bring back life."</font>

809
01:30:01,920 --> 01:30:03,784
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Spreading
death and destruction</i></font>

810
01:30:03,787 --> 01:30:05,027
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>with just the touch
of her hand.</i></font>

811
01:30:06,789 --> 01:30:07,992
<font color="#FFFFFF">Go on.</font>

